high_descs: Move to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up the bread from the counter.
Bring the bread to the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave.
Bring the bread to the table.
Put the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put heated bread on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter on your right.
Pick up a loaf of bread from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the microwave on your left.
Warm the bread in the microwave.
Walk to the table on the other end of the room.
Place the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed loaf of bread on a table.

high_descs: Turn right.  Go to the counter next to the stove.  Turn right and face it.
Pick up the loaf of bread on the counter next to the stove.
Turn around.  Move to the stove and turn and face the stove.
Open the microwave door.  Put the bread in the microwave.  Start the microwave.  Take the bread out of the microwave.
Turn around.  Move towards the door.  Turn right and move to the table.  Turn right and face the table.
Set the bread down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Warm the bread up to put on the table.
